room_title: Escape room "Tualatin Valley Room" by Escape Space Games in Portland
room_description: The Tualatin Valley Room is meant to prepare you for everything that is to come! You will need to harness the skills of both the LEFT and RIGHT side of your brain! Consider this your training for escape room play in Tualatin, OR! You'll need to keep your wits about you if you hope to escape The Valley before your one hour runs out!
